html:
set

Setsthe schema element to the value determined by the values parameter.

merge

Merges the values from the parent, replaced, and replacing schemas. The properties from the values parameter of the last descendant override the other values.

remove

Deletes the element from the schema.

move

Moves the element to a different parent element.

insert

Adds the element to the schema.
